Hi William! How can I assist you today?
I received an email from ClickBank telling me that I will get $2000 credit for registering an NewsBreak ad account through the link in the email, how do I get it after registering my account?

Hi William! To get the $2000 credit after registering your NewsBreak ad account through the ClickBank link, you will need to follow the instructions provided in the email. Typically, this involves verifying your account and possibly entering a promo code or contacting ClickBank support for further assistance. If you have any specific details from the email, please share them so I can provide more precise guidance.
I have contacted ClickBank and they said the $2,000 is ad credit on NewsBreak, you will set up with that credit for me.

Got it, William! To set up your $2,000 ad credit on NewsBreak, you'll need to schedule an onboarding call with our Account Managers for business verification. You can schedule the call through this link: [NewsBreak Advertising Consultation](https://calendly.com/d/z4w-3t3-rkw/newsbreak-advertising-consultation). Once verified, the ad credit will be applied to your account. If you need further assistance, feel free to ask!
I don't need onboarding call, can we communicate via instant messaging, such as Skype.

I understand, William. However, the onboarding call is a required step for business verification to receive the ad credit. This helps ensure that everything is set up correctly and securely. If you have any concerns or need assistance with scheduling the call, please let me know!
